- CC BY-SA 4.0  
  https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/

- CC BY-SA 3.0  
  https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/

- CC0 1.0 Universal  
  https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/

---

## Scope of This File

This file covers **only flag images**.

Application source code, UI design, and original non-image data are
licensed separately and are not covered by this file.

---

## Disclaimer

FlagFinder is an educational and informational project.

The inclusion of historical flags or symbols does not imply endorsement of
any government, ideology, or political entity, past or present.
